A simple defect tracking application to demonstrate how to build applications using Pink.

Steps to setup a database:

- Create a MySQL database.
- Load the schema from Supporting/Data/schema.sql.
- Create a data source for the database in your server.
- Open src/META-INF/persistence.xml and enter the JNDI name of the data source in <jta-data-source>.

Launch the site using this URL:

http://localhost:8080/DTS/app/defect